title: The Absent Minded Professor & Son of Flubber &  Flubber
description:
This is a five-pack of all of the Flubber movies produced. This includes The Absent-Minded professor in Black&White and in Color, Son of Flubber in Black&White and in color, and the new Flubber movie.

There seems to be either no torrents or no seeders for some of these movies, so here they are for your viewing and nostalgia pleasure. Let's make sure these treasures don't disappear!
